    <article class="legal-layout">

      <h2>Common Questions</h2>

      <h3>What does VPN XX do?</h3>
      <p>VPN XX manages subscription URLs and proxy node information. It helps import, refresh, organize, share, and test nodes.</p>

      <h3>Does VPN XX provide VPN servers?</h3>
      <p>No. VPN XX does not sell nodes, provide proxy subscriptions, or operate a VPN traffic network.</p>

      <h3>Why do some speed tests fail?</h3>
      <p>Latency and reachability depend on the protocol, endpoint, network, subscription provider, and whether the imported node supports the app&#39;s test method.</p>

      <h3>How do I delete data?</h3>
      <p>Use the app&#39;s settings to clear local data, restore from iCloud, clear iCloud data, or clear both local and iCloud data.</p>
    </article>
